{"article_id":"AO6zm6uhjDJC8VJX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu 's chief rival said","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he agreed with a smaller party to work together","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to form a new government","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"following national elections last week .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The announcement on Monday by Benny Gantz , leader of the Blue and White Party , dealt a new setback to Netanyahu","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"as he struggles to hold on to power before his upcoming trial on corruption charges .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"In a statement , Gantz said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"he had a good meeting with Avigdor Lieberman , leader of the small Yisrael Beiteinu party .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"`` We discussed questions of fundamental principle","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"and determined","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that we will work together","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"to assemble a government","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"that will pull Israel out of the political deadlock","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"and avert a fourth round of elections , ''","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Gantz said .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"In last week 's election , Israel 's third in less than a year , Netanyahu 's Likud party emerged as the largest party .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"But with his smaller religious and nationalist allies , he secured only 58 seats in parliament , three short of the required 61-seat majority","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"needed","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"to form a new government .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Netanyahu 's opponents ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"led by Gantz ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"control a majority of seats .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"But beyond their shared animosity towards Netanyahu , there are deep divisions between these parties ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"which include Lieberman 's secular , ultra-nationalist party and the Arab-led Joint List .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Gantz 's announcement with Lieberman marked a step","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"towards unifying those anti-Netanyahu forces ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"though it remains unclear whether they can reach a final agreement , much less a deal with Arab politicians .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Lieberman has , in the past , branded Arab political leaders as `` terrorist '' sympathisers .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"`` We 'll continue to discuss the details ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"formulate our common objectives ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and move forward , ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Gantz said .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Netanyahu is desperate to remain as prime minister","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"as he prepares to go on trial on March 17 .","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"He has been charged with fraud , breach of trust , and accepting bribes in connection to a series of scandals","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"that include accepting expensive gifts from wealthy friends and offering to exchange favours with powerful media moguls .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"Netanyahu 's lawyers requested a delay in the start of the trial ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"they need more time","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"to review evidence .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Prosecutors on Monday said","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"they oppose any delays .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Israel 's president , Reuven Rivlin , must decide by next week who to choose as the prime minister-designate .","depth":2},{"id":43,"text":"The president typically chooses the candidate","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"he deems","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"has the best chance","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"of forming a governing coalition .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Netanyahu has defiantly insisted","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"he won last week 's election","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"and accused his opponents of trying to `` steal the elections ''","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"by aligning with Arab-led parties","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"he claimed","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"were hostile to the state .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"`` I promise you ,","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"I am not going anywhere , ''","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Netanyahu said over the weekend .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":111,"left":97,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":87,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":70,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":61,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":0,"right":58,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":58,"left":57,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":57,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":60,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":62,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":8,"right":67,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":66,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":9,"right":65,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":10,"right":64,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":11,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":86,"left":73,"right":85,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":15,"right":72,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":16,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":77,"right":84,"rel